  <br>
  

  
  <strong>Facs:</strong>+353 90 663 2999
  <br> 
  

  
  <strong>Láithreán Gréasáin:</strong> <a href="http://www.welfare.ie/en/Pages/General-Register-Office.aspx">http://www.welfare.ie/en/Pages/General-Register-Office.aspx</a>
  <br>
  

  

  

  
  <strong>R-phost:</strong> <a href="mailto:gro@groireland.ie">gro@groireland.ie</a>
